Package: sabR
Title: Soil Property Raster Tools for Sustainable Advanced Bioeconomy Research Farms
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Meyer", "Bohn", 
           email = "mpbohn@iastate.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for working with locally stored digital soil raster maps developed as part of the Sustainable Advanced Bioeconomy Research (sabR) project. Includes functions for zonal statistics, depth-weighted aggregation, and conversion of raster data to SoilProfileCollection objects.
License: CC-BY-4.0
